1
00:01:10,752 --> 00:01:12,431
=Those Days=

2
00:01:12,431 --> 00:01:14,800
(Adapted from iceread.com novel
"You Xi" by Qingyang Wanxi)

3
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,980
=Episode 35=

4
00:01:18,559 --> 00:01:19,160
Mom.

5
00:01:21,919 --> 00:01:22,520
Mom.

6
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,240
Sorry.

7
00:01:37,399 --> 00:01:39,839
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

8
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,240
Please try again later.

9
00:01:49,679 --> 00:01:50,360
Auntie.

10
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,399
Have you seen where my mom went?

11
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:53,759
Isn't she upstairs?

12
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:54,720
No.

13
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,240
I just saw her.

14
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,520
Minghui's not here either.

15
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:02,360
He came back just now. Messed around,
grabbed a couple of things.

16
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,479
I don't know where he went.

17
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,479
Don't mind him.

18
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,039
You must be hungry.

19
00:02:05,039 --> 00:02:06,039
I will make you something to eat.

20
00:02:06,039 --> 00:02:07,000
No need, Auntie.

21
00:02:07,119 --> 00:02:08,439
I'll call Minghui.

22
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,640
Pick up.

23
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,240
Hello? Minghui?

24
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,320
Have you seen my Mom?

25
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:24,599
Auntie is with me.

26
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:26,999
She asked me to go with her

27
00:02:26,999 --> 00:02:28,360
to see some acupuncture master.

28
00:02:29,599 --> 00:02:31,200
What master? Where did he come from?

29
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,960
In the mountains, it'll take a few days.

30
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,360
Make sure she remembers
to take her medicine.

31
00:02:35,559 --> 00:02:36,839
Okay, I'll take good care of her.

32
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:37,999
Don't worry.

33
00:02:38,279 --> 00:02:39,040
Bye.

34
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,760
Kid, you're something.

35
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:43,420
You can make up stories
on the spot, huh?

36
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,520
Fine.

37
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,159
Poor little baby.

38
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,360
Just born and already has
to suffer so much.

39
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,760
It hurts when I bite myself.

40
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,760
How could surgery not hurt him?

41
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,879
If it hurts, he'll cry.

42
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,320
But crying won't help.

43
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,240
And we won't even know what he means.

44
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,439
It's all my fault.

45
00:03:14,999 --> 00:03:16,119
I am not ambitious.

46
00:03:16,839 --> 00:03:17,800
Not only that,

47
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,480
I also loves spicy strips.

48
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:25,159
Do you think maybe the doctor
made a mistake?

49
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,119
Maybe the extra finger

50
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,599
is actually just a spicy strip.

51
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,559
Jiao.

52
00:03:43,559 --> 00:03:44,559
Call Mommy for dinner.

53
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,200
Mom, come out for dinner.

54
00:03:49,999 --> 00:03:51,719
I'm not hungry, you eat.

55
00:03:52,279 --> 00:03:53,320
You need to eat.

56
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,999
You're not alone now.

57
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,760
Come eat.

58
00:04:04,559 --> 00:04:05,200
Mom.

59
00:04:05,719 --> 00:04:07,839
Does the baby really have six fingers?

60
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:09,439
You...

61
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,360
It's written right there.

62
00:04:14,119 --> 00:04:14,999
Did you take it out?

63
00:04:15,679 --> 00:04:16,839
I'm the Sister.

64
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,320
I have the right to know.

65
00:04:22,359 --> 00:04:23,599
Let me tell you something.

66
00:04:23,919 --> 00:04:25,080
This is a golden finger.

67
00:04:28,239 --> 00:04:29,080
Really.

68
00:04:29,239 --> 00:04:31,039
Lv Dongbin can turn stones into gold.

69
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,239
Lv...

70
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:38,399
Lv Dongbin can turn stones into gold

71
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:41,520
because he's an immortal.

72
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,359
Not because...

73
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:45,200
Not because he had an extra finger.

74
00:04:45,599 --> 00:04:46,640
My daughter's right.

75
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,919
If Jiao says it's a golden finger,
then it is.

76
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,839
Hello, baby.

77
00:05:16,039 --> 00:05:16,960
He kicked me.

78
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:21,239
He likes you.

79
00:05:22,039 --> 00:05:23,159
Tonight I want to sleep

80
00:05:23,159 --> 00:05:24,640
with Mommy and the baby.

81
00:05:25,359 --> 00:05:26,320
Okay.

82
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,159
Baby, look.

83
00:05:28,719 --> 00:05:29,960
I'm your sister.

84
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:31,399
This is Mommy.

85
00:05:32,239 --> 00:05:33,320
I'm Peppa.

86
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,599
You're George.

87
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,599
Our mom is very beautiful.

88
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:41,039
But she's not very gentle.

89
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,719
You need to be careful.

90
00:05:44,799 --> 00:05:46,159
I am going to sleep now.

91
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,399
Good night.

92
00:06:32,799 --> 00:06:33,839
Don't worry.

93
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,479
Didn't the doctor say

94
00:06:36,359 --> 00:06:38,200
he can have surgery after three months?

95
00:06:41,039 --> 00:06:43,159
He's so little but having surgery...

96
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,060
With general anesthesia.

97
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,239
Such a big risk.

98
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:49,399
What if something goes wrong?

99
00:06:52,110 --> 00:06:53,080
What if when he grows up,

100
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:54,599
he blames me?

101
00:06:54,599 --> 00:06:56,560
No, he won't. How could he blame you?

102
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,080
Even if we...

103
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:01,320
Even if we don't do the surgery,
it's fine.

104
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,239
Right?

105
00:07:02,239 --> 00:07:04,399
It's not like the baby
is missing anything.

106
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:06,000
He just has an extra finger.

107
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,599
Six fingers, look.

108
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,479
Six is a very lucky number.

109
00:07:09,479 --> 00:07:10,399
Smooth and successful.

110
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:11,799
Success all the way.

111
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:13,960
And look,

112
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:16,279
I think our baby will
definitely be very lively.

113
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,760
Just like my personality.

114
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,599
You see how he grows "extra branches".

115
00:07:20,039 --> 00:07:20,760
Right?

116
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,599
It's okay.

117
00:07:30,039 --> 00:07:31,479
Everything will be fine.

118
00:07:32,719 --> 00:07:33,599
It's all my fault.

119
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:36,719
Is it because my temper is too bad

120
00:07:36,719 --> 00:07:40,680
that the baby grew an extra finger?

121
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:41,960
It's not your fault.

122
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:43,399
It's mine.

123
00:07:44,919 --> 00:07:45,719
All my fault.

124
00:07:58,399 --> 00:08:00,159
Where exactly are we going?

125
00:08:02,239 --> 00:08:03,960
Stop.

126
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:05,799
It's right here.

127
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:06,799
Where is this?

128
00:08:06,919 --> 00:08:09,479
According to Meiqi's location post,

129
00:08:10,239 --> 00:08:11,599
it should be this place.

130
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:12,880
So?

131
00:08:14,479 --> 00:08:16,799
Lawyer Yao must be working here.

132
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,799
Are you sure?

133
00:08:20,039 --> 00:08:20,599
No.

134
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:23,200
No? Then why did you bring me here now?

135
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,919
It's so late already.

136
00:08:24,919 --> 00:08:26,200
People are off work by now.

137
00:08:26,799 --> 00:08:28,000
We'll just wait here?

138
00:08:28,919 --> 00:08:30,359
We'll come back again tomorrow.

139
00:08:30,599 --> 00:08:31,279
Tomorrow?

140
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,080
Tomorrow.

141
00:08:32,170 --> 00:08:33,950
We'd have to stay one more night
in Shanghai?

142
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,359
Do you have money?

143
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,400
No.

144
00:08:36,479 --> 00:08:37,999
No money, where do we stay?

145
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,879
Don't you have money?

146
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:40,719
Me?

147
00:08:42,810 --> 00:08:45,200
I'm still a kid. Auntie, I'm onl
in 5th year of high school.

148
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,280
How would I have money?

149
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,160
People graduate after 3rd year.

150
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,280
You're already in 5th year.

151
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,680
You must have money.

152
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,639
I don't have money.

153
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,999
Then think of something.

154
00:09:04,599 --> 00:09:05,479
You can do it.

155
00:09:17,599 --> 00:09:18,200
Hello?

156
00:09:19,359 --> 00:09:21,970
Mr. Ni. I want to discuss a business deal
with you.

157
00:09:21,980 --> 00:09:28,860
(Xiushui Hotel)

158
00:09:30,479 --> 00:09:32,160
Xiushui Hotel.

159
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,359
Let's go, Auntie.

160
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:34,960
I'm not staying there.

161
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,599
Then where do you want to stay?

162
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:41,440
I want to stay in a five-star hotel.

163
00:09:42,119 --> 00:09:43,400
A five-star hotel?

164
00:09:43,999 --> 00:09:45,160
Given our situation?

165
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,080
We can't afford a five-star hotel.

166
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,479
Then I'm not staying here either.

167
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:49,639
It's just a place to rest.

168
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:51,440
Just make do. Does it matter that much?

169
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,239
It does.

170
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,160
I'm not staying.

171
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,839
I'm only staying in a five-star hotel.

172
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,359
But we don't have enough money.

173
00:09:57,719 --> 00:09:58,839
You can only stay one night.

174
00:09:59,479 --> 00:10:00,759
We'd even have to share a room.

175
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:02,440
Are you okay with that, Auntie?

176
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,400
I'm fine with it.

177
00:10:03,999 --> 00:10:05,759
I can share a room with you.

178
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,160
What's the big deal?

179
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,759
One night is fine.

180
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,560
Aren't you good at borrowing money?

181
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,999
Then borrow again tomorrow.

182
00:10:12,239 --> 00:10:13,759
Money isn't that easy to borrow.

183
00:10:15,119 --> 00:10:16,350
You talk like you borrowed it.

184
00:10:17,119 --> 00:10:17,999
You borrowed it.

185
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:19,440
Come on.

186
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:20,639
Where?

187
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,719
The five-star hotel, of course.

188
00:10:22,719 --> 00:10:23,359
Let's go.

189
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:24,999
Uh.

190
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,280
Is it really okay for us
to share one room?

191
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,560
What's the problem?

192
00:10:28,999 --> 00:10:30,519
If my third child had lived,

193
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:31,839
he'd be about your age.

194
00:10:31,839 --> 00:10:32,639
It's fine.

195
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:33,950
You'll have to pay me back though.

196
00:10:34,239 --> 00:10:35,519
Why are you so stingy?

197
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:41,560
Mrs. Feng.

198
00:10:42,239 --> 00:10:43,400
You asked to meet me today,

199
00:10:44,599 --> 00:10:46,920
whatever it is, just say it directly.

200
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,080
Yes.

201
00:10:49,719 --> 00:10:50,320
Mr. Wang.

202
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,440
Long time no see.

203
00:10:52,479 --> 00:10:53,119
Well.

204
00:10:53,999 --> 00:10:55,239
The debt our family owed

205
00:10:56,479 --> 00:10:57,719
all paid off.

206
00:10:57,839 --> 00:10:58,719
Did you know?

207
00:10:58,999 --> 00:10:59,759
I'm aware.

208
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,879
It's indeed all settled.

209
00:11:03,839 --> 00:11:05,800
So the reason I invited you today

210
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:08,680
is to talk about a cooperation.

211
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,119
Here's the thing.

212
00:11:11,479 --> 00:11:12,320
Right now in my hands,

213
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,519
I have a batch of high-quality silk.

214
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,080
I want to use this batch

215
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,759
to revive Jianmei Workshop.

216
00:11:20,999 --> 00:11:22,320
I need your help.

217
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,479
I wonder if you're willing

218
00:11:24,479 --> 00:11:25,800
to work with us again.

219
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:28,999
Mrs. Feng.

220
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:31,960
I truly understand your determination

221
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,119
to make a comeback.

222
00:11:33,719 --> 00:11:34,839
But this kind of thing

223
00:11:34,839 --> 00:11:37,879
can't be achieved just by understanding.

224
00:11:38,839 --> 00:11:40,320
Manpower, resources, capital.

225
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:41,999
Which one is easy?

226
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,440
Feng built it step by step,

227
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:46,519
you know how hard

228
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,960
it was.

229
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,800
Even if we take ten thousand steps back,

230
00:11:51,239 --> 00:11:53,200
you have the silk,

231
00:11:53,599 --> 00:11:54,599
you have start-up funds,

232
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,639
but who will run things?

233
00:11:59,080 --> 00:11:59,759
Mr. Wang.

234
00:12:00,359 --> 00:12:01,999
Here's how I see it.

235
00:12:02,599 --> 00:12:04,999
Look, I have the goods now.

236
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:08,080
Jianmei Workshop's machines
are all there.

237
00:12:09,519 --> 00:12:10,800
You watched me

238
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:12,999
build this with Feng.

239
00:12:13,119 --> 00:12:14,119
I have experience.

240
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:16,160
Most importantly,

241
00:12:16,479 --> 00:12:17,960
I have the will.

242
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:20,479
This time I must succeed.

243
00:12:20,479 --> 00:12:21,400
No failure allowed.

244
00:12:22,359 --> 00:12:23,119
As for manpower,

245
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,839
I have it.

246
00:12:25,479 --> 00:12:26,200
I do.

247
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,999
My daughter Meiqi has returned
from her studies in the UK.

248
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,839
After everything she went through,

249
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:37,320
she's completely transformed.

250
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,280
And this is our family business.

251
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:43,080
She'll definitely devote herself
to the workshop.

252
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,680
Young people have seen the world.

253
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,519
They have taste,

254
00:12:47,839 --> 00:12:49,040
and new ideas.

255
00:12:51,599 --> 00:12:52,680
Of course, Mr. Wang.

256
00:12:52,999 --> 00:12:55,680
The most important thing is still you.

257
00:12:57,560 --> 00:13:00,160
If you're willing to help
Feng family once more,

258
00:13:01,119 --> 00:13:01,920
I believe

259
00:13:02,839 --> 00:13:04,119
our Jianmei Workshop

260
00:13:04,119 --> 00:13:06,479
will definitely rise again.

261
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:07,719
Definitely.

262
00:13:10,119 --> 00:13:12,200
Mrs. Feng. You're putting
a lot of pressure on me.

263
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:16,479
How about this?

264
00:13:17,359 --> 00:13:19,400
You prepare a proposal first.

265
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:20,519
I'll take a look.

266
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,400
After I review it,

267
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:24,839
we'll decide on the next step
of cooperation.

268
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:25,879
How about that?

269
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,560
Okay, thank you, Mr. Wang.

270
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,800
I'll send you the proposal
as soon as possible.

271
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,839
Thank you very much.

272
00:13:31,999 --> 00:13:32,639
Mrs. Feng.

273
00:13:33,119 --> 00:13:35,239
It's still too early
to say these things.

274
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:37,560
I'll wait for the proposal.

275
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:38,400
Alright.

276
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,479
I have something else to do,
I'll get going.

277
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:43,359
Okay.

278
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:45,200
Thank you so much.

279
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,239
- Thank you.
- Goodbye.

280
00:13:46,239 --> 00:13:48,359
Thank you. Sorry to trouble you
to come all the way.

281
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:49,239
It's fine.

282
00:13:49,239 --> 00:13:51,119
I'll send you the proposal soon.

283
00:13:51,119 --> 00:13:51,879
Alright.

284
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:52,519
Thanks.

285
00:13:59,479 --> 00:14:00,119
Auntie.

286
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:02,879
Now I understand
