00:37:03,119 --> 00:37:04,320
What are you saying, Mrs. Feng?

859
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:05,880
It's nothing.

860
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:09,639
Mr. and Mrs. Shen.

861
00:37:10,159 --> 00:37:11,079
Thank you.

862
00:37:11,679 --> 00:37:13,599
During our toughest times,

863
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,199
you never left us.

864
00:37:16,679 --> 00:37:18,760
Always supporting and helping us.

865
00:37:19,559 --> 00:37:21,240
Family shouldn't say these things.

866
00:37:21,240 --> 00:37:21,920
Don't worry.

867
00:37:22,639 --> 00:37:24,400
We'll end this kind of

868
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,760
relying on others' home life soon.

869
00:37:26,639 --> 00:37:27,920
We'll move out quickly.

870
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:29,920
Once our factory is up,

871
00:37:30,079 --> 00:37:31,920
we'll buy back our house soon.

872
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:33,519
Don't worry.

873
00:37:34,519 --> 00:37:35,079
Mom,

874
00:37:35,079 --> 00:37:36,920
eat while it's hot,
don't let it get cold.

875
00:37:37,119 --> 00:37:38,679
No, the noodles are too hard.

876
00:37:38,679 --> 00:37:39,400
I'll soak them.

877
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,450
I'll have some soup first.

878
00:37:40,599 --> 00:37:42,039
Then I'll make you another bowl.

879
00:37:42,039 --> 00:37:43,039
No.

880
00:37:43,039 --> 00:37:44,079
Sit down, don't bother.

881
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,360
I'll get some vinegar.

882
00:37:56,199 --> 00:37:56,840
Mom,

883
00:37:57,880 --> 00:37:59,920
what did you mean by what you just said?

884
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,880
I meant nothing.

885
00:38:05,079 --> 00:38:07,119
I support you having the child.

886
00:38:09,639 --> 00:38:11,840
A single mother can still raise a child

887
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,400
healthy and happy.

888
00:38:14,039 --> 00:38:15,039
I know.

889
00:38:16,159 --> 00:38:18,039
But you shouldn't have just said

890
00:38:18,530 --> 00:38:19,840
living under someone else's roof.

891
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,280
Must be uncomfortable
after they heard it.

892
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,280
Without money,
you can't hold your head high.

893
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:27,400
Right now,

894
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:29,320
we've just come here
to stay temporarily.

895
00:38:29,720 --> 00:38:30,679
If it drags on,

896
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,519
they'll definitely feel uncomfortable,

897
00:38:32,519 --> 00:38:33,400
and unhappy.

898
00:38:35,679 --> 00:38:36,320
Meiqi,

899
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,280
this time when I went to Shanghai,

900
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:42,013
I met the first partner

901
00:38:42,037 --> 00:38:45,280
from when your dad
and I started our business.

902
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:48,920
They've already agreed to help us

903
00:38:49,559 --> 00:38:51,559
rebuild the factory.

904
00:38:53,119 --> 00:38:53,920
Why?

905
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:56,440
Starting a factory
isn't just about talking.

906
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:57,519
Why would they help us?

907
00:38:57,519 --> 00:38:59,639
Because of you, because of me,

908
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:02,400
and the inheritance your dad left.

909
00:39:02,599 --> 00:39:05,920
But we've already handled everything
that needed handling.

910
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:08,039
Meiqi,

911
00:39:08,350 --> 00:39:09,400
before I went to Shanghai,

912
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:11,840
I had Minghui accompany me
to Jianmei Workshop.

913
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:12,720
Sure enough,

914
00:39:13,159 --> 00:39:15,039
Feng had left stock there.

915
00:39:15,519 --> 00:39:16,760
Mulberry silk.

916
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:18,280
Look at this.

917
00:39:40,079 --> 00:39:40,720
Mom,

918
00:39:42,240 --> 00:39:44,039
Dad really cared about us.

919
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,119
Meiqi,

920
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,400
with this stock,

921
00:39:51,679 --> 00:39:53,559
we can make a comeback.

922
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,400
But starting a factory is so hard.

923
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,760
How could we do it alone?

924
00:40:01,999 --> 00:40:03,639
Don't underestimate me.

925
00:40:05,119 --> 00:40:06,280
You think I've always been

926
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:08,280
a pampered idle person?

927
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:09,920
Not at all.

928
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:12,599
I followed your dad,

929
00:40:12,599 --> 00:40:15,400
starting from scratch with him.

930
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:17,400
Back then, we had no money.

931
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,240
You know what?

932
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:20,280
We put the goods on the back
of bicycles,

933
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,559
and delivered them by bike.

934
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,999
The stacks were taller than me.

935
00:40:23,999 --> 00:40:25,960
As soon as I got on, the bike tipped.

936
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:27,679
I had to lie over the handlebars

937
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,880
to ride and deliver.

938
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:32,039
Later, when we had a little money,

939
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:34,320
we started hiring trucks.

940
00:40:34,599 --> 00:40:36,360
Each of us guarded a truck,

941
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:38,400
afraid the goods would be swapped.

942
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:40,320
We entertained clients

943
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:42,159
to secure orders.

944
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,519
Dad drank till he was sick, I took over.

945
00:40:45,079 --> 00:40:48,920
That's how our business was built,
order by order.

946
00:40:49,159 --> 00:40:50,559
I didn't know that.

947
00:40:52,559 --> 00:40:54,199
There are many things you don't know.

948
00:40:54,199 --> 00:40:55,199
When we have time later,

949
00:40:55,199 --> 00:40:56,920
I'll tell you slowly.

950
00:41:00,079 --> 00:41:00,800
Meiqi,

951
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,639
are you willing to take another shot

952
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:07,599
with me?

953
00:41:12,119 --> 00:41:14,039
Yes, of course I am, Mom.

954
00:41:15,079 --> 00:41:16,320
But the problem now is,

955
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:19,559
the restaurant is finally on track.

956
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:22,400
Mingzhu and I are fully committed,
so there's no energy left.

957
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:22,920
No.

958
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,519
Meiqi, I've thought it through.

959
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:27,159
You studied abroad
and have seen the world.

960
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,159
Since you were little,

961
00:41:28,159 --> 00:41:29,800
you've been in the factory with your dad.

962
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:31,400
You know the fabrics inside out.

963
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:33,240
You understand everything.

964
00:41:34,039 --> 00:41:36,079
Running a restaurant is just
a temporary measure.

965
00:41:36,079 --> 00:41:37,519
Now the opportunity has come.

966
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:38,760
Let me tell you,

967
00:41:39,240 --> 00:41:41,559
the factory's yearly profit
can't be matched

968
00:41:41,559 --> 00:41:43,840
by that restaurant even in ten years.

969
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:47,400
Meiqi.

970
00:41:48,599 --> 00:41:51,240
Do you want to stay cooped up
in that little restaurant for life?

971
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:54,400
Don't you want to fly higher,

972
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:55,519
and go further?

973
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,039
Now you have a child,

974
00:41:58,039 --> 00:41:59,760
and you've decided to have him.

975
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:03,920
You have a responsibility
to give him the best conditions.

976
00:42:04,199 --> 00:42:06,039
I understand the logic, but

977
00:42:07,519 --> 00:42:09,800
you're asking me now
to leave Mingzhu alone there.

978
00:42:10,999 --> 00:42:13,599
Wouldn't all our efforts be wasted?

979
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,880
Then where does Mingzhu stand?

980
00:42:16,039 --> 00:42:17,920
Their whole family is helping us,

981
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,400
and you want to push her aside now?

982
00:42:19,410 --> 00:42:20,199
What does that mean?

983
00:42:20,199 --> 00:42:21,920
Who says we're leaving her?

984
00:42:22,479 --> 00:42:24,360
Mingzhu will come with us.

985
00:42:24,639 --> 00:42:25,400
Meiqi,

986
00:42:25,639 --> 00:42:27,199
the Feng family's women

987
00:42:27,199 --> 00:42:28,720
will definitely make it work.

988
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,159
It's not like that, Mom.

989
00:42:30,159 --> 00:42:30,920
Then how is it?

990
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:33,150
You said don't let her do it,
so you don't let her do it.

991
00:42:33,199 --> 00:42:35,320
She sold her only house.

992
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,559
Once the factory starts,

993
00:42:36,559 --> 00:42:38,599
she can buy it back quickly.

994
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:40,119
Really.

995
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:42,360
Trust me, Meiqi.

996
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,950
♪The world is noisy♪

997
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:59,930
♪Turning around,
it's already a distant view♪

998
00:43:01,350 --> 00:43:03,230
♪Once I didn’t know what to do♪

999
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:05,310
♪What to hold quietly♪

1000
00:43:05,310 --> 00:43:08,260
♪Like a silent care♪

1001
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:12,530
♪Seasons pass by♪

1002
00:43:12,530 --> 00:43:15,390
♪Time ticks away♪

1003
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,790
♪Seems like I understand a little♪

1004
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:19,570
♪And also let go of some things♪

1005
00:43:19,570 --> 00:43:24,290
♪All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth♪

1006
00:43:24,290 --> 00:43:27,780
♪A long letter is written down♪

1007
00:43:27,930 --> 00:43:31,410
♪Gently spreading love♪

1008
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:35,600
♪To all the forks in fate♪

1009
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:41,230
♪Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved♪
